OL,3,CPlea to Health Secretary to see for
OL,4,Chimself the 'dilapidated' state of
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FLocal politicians in Stockport have
OL,8,Fcalled on the the Health Secretary Wes
OL,9,FStreeting to visit Stepping Hill
OL,10,FHospital after the government said it
OL,11,Fcouldn't afford to pay for long-
OL,12,Fawaited building repairs.
OL,14,FThe site still uses some buildings
OL,15,Fwhich were built in 1905 and recently
OL,16,Fhad to evacuate wards to protect staff
OL,17,Fand patients after ceilings collapsed.
