OL,3,CPlea to Health Secretary to see for
OL,4,Chimself the 'dilapidated' state of
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThe decision not to guarantee money
OL,8,Ffor Stepping Hill Hospital in
OL,9,FStockport has caused fury and the
OL,10,Fleader of Stockport Council, Cllr Mark
OL,11,FHunter, said it's ''frankly
OL,12,Fastonishing'' that it's not a priority
OL,13,Ffor the Government.
OL,15,FIt comes months after hospital bosses
OL,16,Fsaid the bill to fix the dilapidated
OL,17,Festate has reached #130m.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
