OL,3,CPlea to Health Secretary to see for
OL,4,Chimself the 'dilapidated' state of
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FOver the course of just four months
OL,8,Fthis year, Stepping Hill has seen one
OL,9,Fof its major outpatients buildings
OL,10,Fcondemned and demolished, followed by
OL,11,Ftwo 'unexpected and unrelated'
OL,12,Fceilings collapsing in its radiology
OL,13,Fdepartment and its critical care unit.
OL,15,FThose incidents have led to a serious
OL,16,Fdip in the capacity for outpatients
OL,17,Fappointments and the hospital's
OL,18,Fintensive care department being out of
OL,19,Faction for days.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
