OL,4,Chimself the 'dilapidated' state of
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FCouncillors in Stockport passed a
OL,8,Fcross-party motion calling on the
OL,9,FGovernment to provide urgent funds to
OL,10,Frestore the site.
OL,12,FCllr Hunter, a Liberal Democrat, said:
OL,13,F"We are beyond disappointed at the
OL,14,Flatest U-turn by the Labour government.
OL,16,F"Our motion was supported by all
OL,17,Fparties in the chamber, where many
OL,18,Fmembers spoke of the poor state of
OL,19,Fdisrepair the hospital is in.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
