OL,3,CPlea to Health Secretary to see for
OL,4,Chimself the 'dilapidated' state of
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,F"It is quite frankly astonishing that
OL,8,Fgiven the circumstances, that this
OL,9,Fisn't a priority for the Government. "
OL,11,FThe Liberal Democrat motion was passed
OL,12,Fwith an amendment from Stockport
OL,13,FLabour that acknowledged the Mr
OL,14,FStreetings previous commitment to
OL,15,Fprovide the money the NHS needs
OL,16,Fnationally, but urged him to
OL,17,Fprioritise Stepping Hill, given the
OL,18,Fextent of the repairs needed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
