OL,3,CPlea to Health Secretary to see for
OL,4,Chimself the 'dilapidated' state of
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FA Department for Health and Social
OL,8,FCare spokesperson said: "We have
OL,9,Finherited a broken NHS, with many
OL,10,Fhospitals in a state of disrepair,
OL,11,Fmeaning patients have not been able to
OL,12,Faccess the care they so desperately
OL,13,Fneed.
OL,15,F"Repairing and rebuilding our
OL,16,Fcrumbling hospital estate is a vital
OL,17,Fpart of our ambition to create an NHS
OL,18,Fthat is fit for the future through our
OL,19,F10-Year Health Plan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
