OL,3,CPlea to Health Secretary to see for
OL,4,Chimself the 'dilapidated' state of
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,F"We recognise the importance of
OL,8,Fstrategic, value-for-money capital
OL,9,Finvestments to get the NHS back on its
OL,10,Ffeet.
OL,12,F"As well as vital reform, we will
OL,13,Fensure the NHS has the funding it
OL,14,Fneeds as we build a health service fit
OL,15,Ffor the future."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
