OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FEarlier this week Stockport's Labour
OL,8,FMP Navendu Mishra, who has been
OL,9,Fraising the problems at Stepping Hill
OL,10,Fin Parliament for years said he would
OL,11,Fbe speaking to the health secretary
OL,12,Fabout the lack of funding.
OL,14,FMr Mishra said: "I'll be telling the
OL,15,Fhealth secretary that I want the
OL,16,Fappropriate funding to resolve the
OL,17,Fdilapidated estate issues.
